title: and DJ Duffey
description:
DJ Duffey brings her mad music and baller skills to the show as she explains what it means to follow your dreams, never give up, and slay career and motherhood! She talks about getting her start DJ’ing, meeting French Montana, and learning artist management. She also shares what it’s like being a woman in a male-dominated industry, earning and demanding respect, and passing knowledge to aspiring music makers.
